       'Snooze		4.3.0
       <bobbit>		4.1.2  (DejaNews suggests it's dead)
       AOS		4.1.1  (PDP-10 mnemonic; no longer live)
       CTY		4.1.1  (the OSs that used this are 15 years dead)
       DEChead		4.1.0  (obs. now that DEC is gone)
